Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元气  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗塞塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小可奈  看到这个场景之后是不是有点兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但Gunvarrel的主题是爱与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小可奈  小可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
